Indonesia is Best Emerging Market, Blackstone’s Studzinski Says

-- B y   C h r i s   K a y
-- 
2011-03-17T09:06:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/indonesia-is-best-emerging-market-blackstone-s-studzinski-says.html
  Indonesia  is the best emerging
market because of prospective growth in metals, mining and
agriculture, said John Studzinski, senior managing director of
Blackstone Group LP.  “Agriculture will be increasingly important given
commodity prices,” Studzinski said at the Bloomberg Link Hedge
Fund Conference in  London  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:  Chris Kay  in London at   ckay5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at   gserkin@bloomberg.net . 